019-11-04T04:54:06.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"ba397a8abf1642592b28be60f70d79e10d357659","tid":1692261,"uid":147317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f2e1d296c2076dfe2ce88abadaf170a432a788b","tid":1692261,"uid":147317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:54:06.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:54:33.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"ab89797616a2cd266cdb1f708bc3d6df67654024","tid":1692261,"uid":220519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:54:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b885ebd4f0e32e241c728ba52a2a99195afff3d0","tid":1692261,"uid":147317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:55:16.000Z","msg":"還拖"},{"pid":"3c26ef00581334d1ceca4e0543169e9b30c398ef","tid":1692261,"uid":147317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:56:01.000Z","msg":"曱甴平"},{"pid":"b2eced5659ccf5efccab5700136952b1865364c7","tid":1692261,"uid":69629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:56:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"375ae05f16ab4ffe66f1b813fa71ffb2cfea31e5","tid":1692261,"uid":147317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:57:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a67a199b014820098b8c1906af5c7cbd98eef1ed","tid":1692261,"uid":147317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:58:05.000Z","msg":"曱甴平"},{"pid":"0da6e40bc52c9204b2f4ab140feb239ab35f7c4d","tid":1692261,"uid":321631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:59:28.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1378afe0e7c96bddcc0b86f19f0db66bf294e510","tid":1692261,"uid":237581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:59:51.000Z","msg":"【二百萬三罷聯合陣線】<br />\n大家怨完呻完，想罷工，想了解點實行嘅，<br />\n可以入Channel參考吓。<br />\n成日話得我罷有咩用，咁俾多啲人都了解吓吖。<br />\n<br />\n⚠️常見問題⚠️<br />\n1. 幾時罷工呀？<br />\n其實罷工有好多前期準備工作，唔係定個日子就可以罷。一來要處理錢嘅問題，需要有罷工基金support，而罷工基金往往係由工會處理返自己個行業。二來要處理邊際成本嘅問題，例如成間公司得一個人罷，甚至有藍絲篤灰，老闆要炒話咁易，但如果成間公司有一半人罷工就好唔同。<br />\n<br />\n2. 咁點樣處理上述講嘅問題？<br />\n罷工好多時會有前期嘅行業行動，例如搵一日係網上call支持罷工嘅人集體dress code或者一齊戴朵花，又或者85三罷前嘅行業集會，咁你就可以由網絡延伸到real contact，知道實質你所處嘅職場有幾多係自己人，繼而組成組織，由自己working place去到隔離公司，甚至成個地區或行業。另一個方法就係工會，以成為會員嘅方式組成real contact，再用工會名義發起罷工。<br />\n<br />\n3. 我可以做啲咩？<br />\n幫手reach你自己行業嘅人，或者參與成立你所屬行業嘅工會。仲有share呢個群組出去，等呢度可以凝聚到更多有意有心罷工嘅人。<br />\n成立工會程序可參照 <a href=\"https://t.me/hkonstrike/63\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike%2F63&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfj%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=360f316b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkonstrike/63</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 罷工基金點搞好？<br />\n目前主要有兩種聲音，一係眾籌，二係工會自己搞返自己行業嘅罷工基金。前者問題在於好難確認申請人係咪真係參與罷工定呃基金，而且如果個個行業人人都申請得，要處理極龐大嘅行政以及法律程序。相較之下，如果工會處理自身罷工基金可以免卻基金被濫用嘅問題，因為要會員先可以申請。當然，基金仍然需要好多討論。<br />\n<br />\n5. 呢個群組有咩用？<br />\n再次強調每個行業嘅組織、籌備工會或者工業行動要返返去自己個行業嗰度傾。但正因為行業太多，每個情況都唔同，所以呢個群組可以俾大家互通消息，最快知道各個行業嘅情況。同埋俾有心搞三罷嘅人可以係度集中討論。<br />\n<br />\n⚠️現設以下分台⚠️<br />\n三罷文宣小組 <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/OUHilRRJw8V58N8AmwOrYw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FOUHilRRJw8V58N8AmwOrYw&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfj%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=2feea7e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/OUHilRRJw8V58N8AmwOrYw</a><br />\n罷工基金討論台 <a href=\"https://t.me/hkstrikefund\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkstrikefund&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfj%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=0dd3d829\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkstrikefund</a><br />\n<br />\n🔴二百萬三罷聯合陣線🔴<br />\n抗爭 | 工會  | 罷工 | 行業行動<br />\n<br />\n頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/hkonstrike\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfj%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=4f8ee264\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkonstrike</a><br />\n公海 <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/FhM2GRbY1ThsEzrnbEyduA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FFhM2GRbY1ThsEzrnbEyduA&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfj%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=19d61f89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/FhM2GRbY1ThsEzrnbEyduA</a><br />\n(必讀)群組須知及group list <a href=\"https://t.me/hkonstrike/61\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike%2F61&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfj%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=f3ce690c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkonstrike/61</a>"},{"pid":"fda5c8542797413e0fd4671baa47aa9e1195bddc","tid":1692261,"uid":303674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:00:30.000Z","msg":"曱甴平<br />\n曱平<br />\n甴平<br />\n曱甴近平<br />\n甴近平<br />\n曱近平"},{"pid":"4706851270d7f448a6e7b626cca2bf90c5818cd9","tid":1692261,"uid":147317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:01:20.000Z","msg":"曱甴平"},{"pid":"ebee5f1113afd65159c9892a58769fd5ae4b1944","tid":1692261,"uid":283133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:03:03.000Z","msg":"重有moko?"},{"pid":"054b7e851580308cdfb990c98ec27343672da519","tid":1692261,"uid":303674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:05:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d804f183d4b71c1e8d538ff87cf4872782529dc","tid":1692261,"uid":69629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:09:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"861cb4a1e0cb803bd263034a4d889a43a7fd1813","tid":1692261,"uid":13514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:24:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0bf292bbf380562ef47fdcfff667d93e33c802ae","tid":1692261,"uid":